  <prompt>
    Close ledger entry RB-T070-01 by adding `cancellationToken.ThrowIfCancellationRequested();` to the THREE public async
    methods of `AgentConversationService` in `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Api/Agent/AgentConversationService.cs`:
    `GetOrCreateContextAsync` (~line 40), `UpdateContextAsync` (~line 69), `RemoveContextAsync` (~line 121).

    Same anti-pattern as RB-T034-01 (task 031). Production fix per ledger Recommended Fix section: add the
    ThrowIfCancellationRequested call as the FIRST statement of each method.

    Test impact: 3 Skip'd tests
    (`GetOrCreateContextAsync_RespectsCancellationToken`, `UpdateContextAsync_RespectsCancellationToken`,
    `RemoveContextAsync_RespectsCancellationToken`) flip Skip -> Pass.
    Per NFR-04: commit message MUST cite "RB-T070-01" + resolution mode `repaired`.
  </prompt>

